description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Gaston purrs with a rating of 64, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 192, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 2 for North, 5 for East, 1 for South, and 5 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60643-25150-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [192 Votes, Top 5% Score]
